'''Restimar Mining Corporation''' was a [[Mining/Legends|mining]] company that existed during the final years of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Old Republic]]. They were known to operate in the [[Cularin system/Legends|Cularin system]]; sending a research team to [[Tilnes]], the [[Moon/Legends|moon]] of [[Cularin/Legends|Cularin]].

